[gd_resource type="Theme" load_steps=12 format=3 uid="uid://uy3znkll7jlqy"]

; Shared menu theme — the teal/navy button language for the main menu, settings screen,
; and debug navigator. Applied at each of those screen roots, so it never touches the in-game
; HUD (which keeps its own chrome styles). Three button looks:
;   Button         — secondary navy card (default for every button on these screens)
;   PrimaryButton  — filled teal call-to-action (Play, Resume, Done)
;   DangerButton   — red-outlined destructive (Quit to Menu)

